# Skybox Cube Mesh (Inside-Out Winding)
# Centered at (0,0,0) with coordinates from -1 to 1

# Vertex Positions (v x y z)
v -1.0  1.0  1.0
v  1.0  1.0  1.0
v  1.0 -1.0  1.0
v -1.0 -1.0  1.0
v -1.0  1.0 -1.0
v  1.0  1.0 -1.0
v  1.0 -1.0 -1.0
v -1.0 -1.0 -1.0

# Face Indices (f v1 v2 v3) - Wound to face inward
# Front Face
f 1 3 2
f 1 4 3
# Right Face
f 2 7 6
f 2 3 7
# Back Face
f 6 8 5
f 6 7 8
# Left Face
f 5 4 1
f 5 8 4
# Top Face
f 5 2 6
f 5 1 2
# Bottom Face
f 4 7 3
f 4 8 7